{"type": "article", "id": 46581, "title": "Nike 要开设瑜伽专区，以及，来看 CHANEL 和 adidas 的联名 ︳浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最好看和最重要的新闻。", "date": "2017-10-27T03:32:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 45052, "name": "CHANEL"}, {"id": 45053, "name": "stussy"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 16950, "name": "Columbia"}, {"id": 5228, "name": "UGG"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171027111347LzrspyA6thYnqUNf.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2017/10/26/nike-reportedly-set-to-open-yoga-pant-studios-in-5000-stores.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Nike 要开设瑜伽专区</strong></a> ︳周四，彭博社的一篇报道称，Nike 将在 11 月 1 日起，在旗下的 5000 多家门店内开设运动女裤专卖区“pant studios”，该区域主要售卖运动胸罩和瑜伽裤等女性运动服饰。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/columbia-sportswear-third-quarter-sales-inch-up-raises-guidance-11037354/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Columbia 第三季度净利润增长 5%，超过预期</strong></a> ︳截止至 9 月 30 日的三个月内，户外运动服饰品牌 Columbia 的销售额与去年几乎持平，为 7.47 亿美元。但它的净利润增长了 5%，至 8770 万美元，超过了此前的预期。</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/business/earnings/ugg-revenues-deckers-earning-q2-company-sale-448923/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>UGG 母公司利润大涨近 25%，公司出售计划搁置</strong></a> ︳截止至 9 月 30 日的第二季度，UGG 的母公司 Deckers 销售额略有下降，减少了 0.7% 至 4.85 亿美元，营业利润则同比大涨 24.8% 至 6740 万美元。Deckers 预计，2018 财年全年销售额增幅约在 1% 至 2% 之间。Deckers 在半年前开始寻求出售，据称有 90 多位潜在买家，但一直未达成交易。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>CHANEL 和 adidas originals 的联名，看起来是真的了。<br></p><p>继 Thom Browne 之后，CHANEL 将在 10 月 30 日正式接管法国买手店 colette。<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/pharrell-chanel-adidas-originals-hu-nmd-trial-colette-release\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel x Pharrell x adidas Originals 三方联名的 Hu NMD Trial </a>也将在该期间登场。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710271101032i0yX8Cf3vtr5mRQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667247\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>街头品牌<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/26/stussy-holiday-2017/#slide-27\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Stüssy </a>发布 2017 假日系列。穿插着花卉、蘑菇、格纹元素的飞行员夹克、羊毛外套看起来还不错。<br> </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110131zyIoVK9ENgMChpj7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710271101328qIy539aTxkpe7Pn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110133XYZNQyVIPUocKsDw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110135fntj0EK2r6SdBvm3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110135DwMb24LTcR6voCFX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110135Fqopf0YTnkEw7cSU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110136EQlV5tBisoNZm4u1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110138Wp4bYTJdXwBioOEP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110140SK1qsxNbykQV0GCW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110142cIYlGzdu1N5PA9Bg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110144umxW62Isgnad8DUl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110145Gk9xZhUBcEldvCaR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110146ZGXiR1kYB29Ima04.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110146Ccw2xF9oMifVBEPs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110147C0kiTy2MX1jdpagh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110147Lld1PhtvIC0sRZB4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110149IUKEXb35yhcMo1v2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110150cRvtOMZFSq4mabEg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110151aw6l8hXGF2ueVjWT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/26/opening-ceremony-columbia-fall-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Opening Ceremony 与 Columbia 首次合作</a>，居然把 Columbia 的冲锋衣变好看了... </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710271107579bmMLyOi84u7TYUo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110801cSZW5wbKkRTdvMQD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110801xlkgR8QJKhe6Bqap.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110803nRhXrzVuqj9lOb64.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110805E8rhMa61q7nlQOiS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110805wZeuAf49dY3VpD7z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110806y8dsg3JqowY10ORB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Balenciaga 的爆款<a href=\"http://thesource.com/2017/10/26/balenciaga-set-drop-cream-triple-s-sneaker/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Triple S</a> 出了款温柔的奶油配色 Cream。 </p><p>这双鞋将于 10 月 30 日登陆 END. 等指定店铺，定价为 745 美元，<a href=\"https://launches.endclothing.com/product/balenciaga-vintage-triple-sole-sneaker-483546-wo6f1-9000\" rel=\"nofollow\">抽签通道</a>现已开启。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110901XY8od1FOTemMC46G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110829GOEySTvmdkIDPol0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110830irAQv2EjVfKJqh3b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110830CqfcbUdPG6KOua8z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-10-26/gucci-yuko-higuchi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 与日本人气插画家樋口裕子合</a>作，将从 12 月开始，发售一个以猫为主角的男女童装及配饰系列。<br></p><p>樋口裕子擅长画拟人化的猫，也是近些年日本最热门的插画家之一，她与资生堂、优衣库都有过合作。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110925LslCbJERYnTMfv1w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710271109263F2cijQLX0T5JYVZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110926YWsgbPdNFUDZLr0A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110926BDbk2aflXdSM7xAO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110926HRrFCeiaDY5xLknB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110930sRQ8hrS7KkGaePoZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110927SguIftyLpjPRQAWH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110930FUxKE2yAl0IjYRVW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110944iG29sRN4rJfvMPzO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110944P0ORwJfrnih8eqYG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110945Jlm4ak6PEQXdijI9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110945BMw8Xc13CQr7mKG4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710271109464JqQcmvzjAgNGPRk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110948oqYTsy8PWxQXf0mR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110948sMkmO3hXeEUbyp19.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110946ciR7USmOnTxDrfZW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171027110946MFolO6rCaBLIRA8s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334118\